# Belt-and-braces: this repo is public and has no build step, so any secret that
# lands here ships to the browser and to GitHub. The Supabase *anon* key is
# meant to be public and lives in js/supabase-config.js; the *service_role* key
# must never be committed anywhere, in any form.
